<center>[[File:en/Patches-interface.png|center|frame|1. - The Configure patches window; Interface]]</center>

====Show vehicle speed in status bar====
Whether or not the vehicle [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Show vehicle speed|speed is shown]] in the vehicle window status bar, where you can stop or make a train go.

====Always show long date in status bar====
Shows the [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Long date in status bar|full date]] all the time rather than just in pause mode.

====Show finances window at the end of the year====
Whether or not the [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Show finances at end of year|finances window]] is shown at the end of the year.

====Pan window when mouse is at the edge====
When the mouse is at the edge of the window the view will [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Autoscroll|scroll]] when this is on.

====Duration of error messages====
How long [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Error message duration|error messages are shown]] for in seconds.